      </structure>
    </statement>
    <statement id="6.txt-3">
      <text>blades oblong-oblanceolate, 2.5–23 cm, bases cuneate, margins pinnately lobed (lobes ovate), spinulose-dentate, apices acute, faces hirtellous and/or finely stipitate-glandular.</text>
      <structure id="o12429" name="blade">
